But we’ve added a beautiful twist, using a special 2-phase anodizing process to create stunning golden edge highlights. To complete this sophisticated new theme, we’ve added a unique gold ASUS logo and given the keyboard a matching gold backlight.

productBaseInfoV1.title: HP G Series Core i3 5th Gen - (4 GB/500 GB HDD/DOS) 240 G5 Y1S93PA Laptop(14 inch, Black, 1.9kg kg)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The 240 G5 (Y1S93PA)(i3 5th Gen/4GB/500GB/DOS) is a laptop manufactured by HP, sporting a 14 inch 1366 x 768 pixels screen. This machine features a Intel Core i3 (5th Gen) running at 2GHz. Complementing the processor is 4GB of RAM of the DDR3 variety. To store your apps, music, videos etc, there's a 500GB Hard Drive (HDD). HP states that the rotational speed of the hard disk is set at 5400 RPM. The legacy of USB 2.0 lives on with this machine, as it features that port. With transfer speeds that are 10 times faster than USB 2.0, it also has USB 3.0 compatibility. While using CDs and DVDs may not be the most common practice today, this one is versatile enough to allow the same using its optical drive bay. You can append the storage of this machine using the following media cards: SD, SDHC, SDXC. All elements rendered on the screen are thanks to its Intel HD Graphics 5500 graphics processor. In order to connect to audio equipment like your headphones, these are the included ports: Headphone + Microphone Combo Jack. With Stereo Speakers, we're hoping consuming multimedia on this one would be a wholesome experience. You can access the internet without wires using WiFi on this machine. To use gadgets like a Bluetooth headset or speaker, it is equipped with Bluetooth. If you have an HDMI cable, you can use it to connect to the HDMI port. Connecting to any projector is possible because of the VGA port. For your consideration, it's weight measures in at 1.9 kg. You can expect a battery life of 7 hours. Sitting underneath the display, this one sports a QWERTY type of keyboard. When you buy this machine, you get DOS built in. For 1 Year from your purchase date, this computer will be covered under warranty.

This notebook comes with 39.62 cm Acer CineCrystal LED-backlit TFT LCD display which has a resolution of 1366x768 pixels. Enjoy watching your favourite videos and TV shows in clear, rich details. This notebook is Wi-Fi enabled, allowing you to connect to wireless internet networks smoothly. You can directly connect the notebook to your modem via LAN as it comes with a Gigabit Ethernet port. With 1 TB storage space, you can easily store all your photos, music, movies and documents in this Acer device.

And when you throw wide viewing angles and exceptional color reproduction into the mix, every visual task is made easier. Entertainment is simply more awesome with S15!
